00:31:25,660 --> 00:31:29,740
 this morning, this chorus does it all for me.

451
00:31:29,740 --> 00:31:33,060
 Look at these words and my friends,

452
00:31:33,060 --> 00:31:35,660
 just come to the altar and say,

453
00:31:35,660 --> 00:31:40,660
 Lord, I need your forgiveness.

454
00:31:40,660 --> 00:31:42,340
 Come into my life.

